title: 4 Bed/3 Bath SF in Plymouth
posting_body: ['Available now.', 'Another new listing brought to you by The Feland Team and Renters Warehouse.', 'This multi-level single family home is on a cul-de-sac and has a park in the back.', 'The main level features an eat-in kitchen with updated appliances, center island with a breakfast bar and lots of cabinet and counter space plus access to the private deck complete with gas grill.', "Next to the kitchen, the formal dining area flows to a great 3 season porch with a gas fireplace with it's own access to back deck.", 'Upstairs there is a formal living room and a master suite including a walk-in closet and a 3/4 private bath plus a full bathroom and 2 additional bedrooms.', 'The lower level includes a family room with a gas fireplace, a walk-out recreation room with a wet bar, a fourth bedroom, bathroom and laundry area.', 'Includes an oversized two car garage and a great backyard including a vegetable garden bed.', 'No pets please.', 'Tenant pays all utilities and is responsible for lawn care and snow removal.', 'Please note there is a $55 application fee.', 'Also, all properties have a one-time $199 lease admin fee and a monthly processing fee of 1% of the rent.', 'This home is not currently qualified for housing assistance programs such as section 8.', 'To book a showing on this property, or view the video tour, go to <URL> and scroll down to the property of interest.']
